Text: I recomend 'The Talmud Jmmanuel' text and material, for information about the original source for the Jesus story/NT Gospels etc.  This is along the 'Ancient Aliens' kind of thinking/acceptance - that Jesus was a prophet/UFO contactee and was seeded via an Angel/ET.  The Jesus miracles remain intact, but what Jesus taught, is altogether different from what Christianity teaches - which is hardly suprising at all..
